snippet.textDisplay:
Malik .. We were used to listen this song..
Its been a decade and Im still listening to this song all alone..
I told you before 'Any mien itna time nai lgaya karo'
Tum ney is bar boht dair kar di hai wapis any mien or wo bhi beghair btaye..
Mien ab muntezir nai raha.. Haan sub sath lekar chal raw hoon.. Or aisy e lekar chalta rahoonga..
Mujhy pta hai kisi din zindagi ki fursutoon mien tumhen waqt mily ga to tum is song ko sun'ny zaroor aogi..
Kuch e dinoon ki baat hai.. Phir tumhary shehr say hotty hvy ek shaam guzar k chala jaonga pakistan say..
Ager itefaaq say daikh bhi lena ye comment to ab mat chali ana wo sub kureedny..
Jesy chal raw hai chaly rehny do..
- Syed Intezar Mehdi
28th September 2024 weekend saturday
12:50 pm DIK KP
